  <description><![CDATA[<h2><span class="TextRun SCXW31311407 BCX8" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW31311407 BCX8">Enjoy a few days in the beautiful waterside city of Bergen with plenty of cultural sites to explore on foot followed by adventure in Voss. This dynamic, Norwegian town is a great base for anyone wanting to discover Norway’s natural gems and scenic views.</span></span></h2>
<p><span class="TextRun SCXW31311407 BCX8" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW31311407 BCX8">This is the perfect multi-centre holiday for those wanting </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW31311407 BCX8">to see two sides to <a data-udi="umb://document/286d71b6bae94f84a7ac63448c015f54" href="/{localLink:umb://document/286d71b6bae94f84a7ac63448c015f54}" title="Norway" data-anchor="#">Norway</a>. The charming city of <a data-udi="umb://document/d517b2c21fa94eb096a3bcb6b7e933c5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d517b2c21fa94eb096a3bcb6b7e933c5}" title="Bergen" data-anchor="#">Bergen</a> has plenty of galleries, </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW31311407 BCX8">museums</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW31311407 BCX8"> and day trips to try </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW31311407 BCX8">whereas</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW31311407 BCX8"> <a data-udi="umb://document/3bff04d1881648b5a6163cdd11cfb562" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3bff04d1881648b5a6163cdd11cfb562}" title="Voss" data-anchor="#">Voss</a> is an escape to nature. Voss is in a great position, positioned between Bergen and the fjords with plenty of activities to enjoy in the town.</span></span></p>
<h3><span data-contrast="auto">Guide price from: £1,220pp*</span></h3>
<h3><span data-contrast="auto">Your multi-centre holiday options:</span><span data-contrast="auto"> </span><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}"> </span></h3>
<ul>
<li>A choice of durations in your chosen hotels</li>
<li><span data-contrast="auto">Any day arrivals</span></li>
</ul>
<h3><span data-contrast="auto">Your holiday includes</span></h3>
<ul>
<li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="2" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;multilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><span data-contrast="auto">Return flights from the UK</span></li>
<li>Return airport transfers (direct) to and from your chosen hotels</li>
<li>Transfers between your chosen destinations</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>
<h2 style="text-align: center;">How to Book Your Multi-Centre Holiday</h2>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>Simply give us a call to book your multi-centre holiday. Flights, hotel and transport? Consider it done. Dial in and let our experts plan your dream getaway. </span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call Us to Book Today</a></p>
<p><em>*Prices are based on 2 people sharing for 4 nights in a Twin Room at Thon Hotel Bristol Bergen, Bergen, and 3 nights in a Twin Standard Railway Room at Fleischer's Hotel, Voss, with train transfers between resorts, departing on the 1st of June 25 from London Gatwick airport. Supplements for alternative flights, flight routes, and room types may apply. Prices are correct at the time of publishing on 21/11/24 but are subject to change based on availability. Please call for the most up-to-date pricing and availability before booking.</em></p>]]></description>
