  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p><span class="TextRun SCXW31311407 BCX8" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW31311407 BCX8">This is the perfect multi-centre holiday for those wanting </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW31311407 BCX8">to see two sides to Norway. The charming city of Bergen has plenty of galleries, </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW31311407 BCX8">museums</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW31311407 BCX8"> and day trips to try </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW31311407 BCX8">whereas</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW31311407 BCX8"> Voss is an escape to nature.</span></span></p>]]></listingDescription>
